\c 23
\nb
\v 1 UDavida esemdala esanele ngensuku\x + 29.28. 2 Lan. 24.15.\x* wamisa uSolomoni indodana yakhe ukuthi abe yinkosi phezu kukaIsrayeli\x + 28.5. 29.22. 1 Kho. 1.33-39.\x*.
\s Izigaba zabapristi lezamaLevi lemisebenzi yazo
\p
\v 2 Wasebuthanisa zonke induna zakoIsrayeli labapristi lamaLevi.
\v 3 AmaLevi asebalwa kusukela koleminyaka engamatshumi amathathu kusiya phezulu\x + Nani 4.3.\x*; lenani lawo, ngamakhanda awo\x + 23.24. Eks. 16.16. Nani 1.2.\x*, ngamadoda, laba zinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amathathu lesificaminwembili\x + Nani 4.47,48.\x*.
\v 4 Kula kwakulezinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amabili lane okuqondisa umsebenzi wendlu yeN\nd kosi\nd*; lezinduna labahluleli abayizinkulungwane eziyisithupha\x + 26.29. Dute. 16.18. 2 Lan. 19.8.\x*;
\v 5 labagcini bamasango abayizinkulungwane ezine; labadumisi beN\nd kosi\nd* abayizinkulungwane ezine ngezinto engizenzele ukudumisa\x + 2 Lan. 29.25,26. Neh. 12.36. Amos 6.5.\x*\add , watsho uDavida\x + Eks. 18.4.\x*\add*.
\v 6 UDavida wasewehlukanisa ngezigaba\x + 2 Lan. 8.14. 23.18. 29.25. 35.4.\x*, ngokwamadodana kaLevi, oGerishoni, uKohathi, loMerari\x + 15.5.\x*.
\p
\v 7 KumaGerishoni kwakungoLadani loShimeyi\x + 26.21,22.\x*.
\v 8 Amadodana kaLadani: OJehiyeli inhloko\x + 15.18. 29.8. 26.21.\x*, loZethamu\x + 26.21,22.\x*, loJoweli, emathathu\x + 26.21,22.\x*.
\v 9 Amadodana kaShimeyi: OShelomithi loHaziyeli loHarani, emathathu. La ayezinhloko zaboyise koLadani.
\v 10 Lamadodana kaShimeyi\x + 23.7.\x*: OJahathi, uZiza, loJewushi, loBeriya. La ayengamadodana kaShimeyi, emane.
\v 11 LoJahathi wayeyinhloko, loZiza engowesibili; kodwa uJewushi loBeriya babengelabantwana abanengi, ngakho babesendlini yaboyise ngokubalwa kanye.
\p
\v 12 Amadodana kaKohathi: OAmramu, uIzihari, uHebroni, loUziyeli, emane\x + 6.18. 26.23. Eks. 6.18. Nani 3.19.\x*.
\v 13 Amadodana kaAmramu: OAroni loMozisi\x + Eks. 6.20.\x*. UAroni wehlukaniselwa-ke\x + Eks. 28.1.\x* ukungcwelisa izinto ezingcwelengcwele, yena lamadodana akhe, kuze kube nininini\x + Eks. 40.10.\x*, ukutshisa impepha phambi kweN\nd kosi\x + Eks. 30.7. Nani 16.40. 1 Sam. 2.28.\x*\nd*, ukuyikhonza\x + Dute. 21.5.\x*, lokubusisa ngebizo layo kuze kube nininini\x + Nani 6.23.\x*\x + Dute. 21.5.\x*.
\v 14 NgoMozisi umuntu kaNkulunkulu\x + Dute. 33.1.\x*, amadodana akhe abizwa ngaphansi kwesizwe sakoLevi\x + 26.23-25.\x*.
\v 15 Amadodana kaMozisi: OGereshoma loEliyezeri\x + Eks. 2.22. 18.3,4.\x*.
\v 16 Amadodana kaGereshoma: UShebuweli inhloko\x + 26.24.\x*.
\v 17 Lamadodana kaEliyezeri ayenguRehabhiya inhloko\x + 26.25.\x*; uEliyezeri wayengelawo-ke amanye amadodana, kodwa amadodana kaRehabhiya ayemanengi okwedlulisayo.
\v 18 Amadodana kaIzihari: UShelomithi inhloko.
\v 19 Amadodana kaHebroni: OJeriya inhloko, uAmariya owesibili, uJahaziyeli owesithathu, uJekameyamu owesine\x + 24.23. 26.31.\x*.
\v 20 Amadodana kaUziyeli: OMika inhloko\x + 24.24,25.\x*, loIshiya owesibili\x + 24.24,25.\x*.
\p
\v 21 Amadodana kaMerari: OMahli loMushi\x + 6.19,29. 24.26. Eks. 6.19. Nani 26.58.\x*. Amadodana kaMahli: OEleyazare loKishi\x + 24.29.\x*.
\v 22 UEleyazare wasesifa, wayengelamadodana kodwa amadodakazi\x + 24.28.\x*; amadodana kaKishi, abafowabo, asewathatha\x + Nani 36.6,8.\x*.
\v 23 Amadodana kaMushi: OMahli loEderi loJeremothi, emathathu\x + 24.30. 6.47.\x*.
\p
\v 24 La ngamadodana kaLevi ngendlu yaboyise\x + Nani 10.17,21.\x*, inhloko zaboyise, ngokubalwa kwawo, ngenani lamabizo, ngamakhanda awo, esenza umsebenzi wenkonzo yendlu yeN\nd kosi\x + Nani 1.22.\x*\nd*, kusukela koleminyaka engamatshumi amabili kusiya phezulu\x + 23.3,27. Nani 1.3. 2 Lan. 31.17. Ezra 3.8. Nani 4.3. 8.24.\x*.
\v 25 Ngoba uDavida wathi: IN\nd kosi\nd*, uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli, ibanikile abantu bayo ukuphumula, bazahlala eJerusalema kuze kube sephakadeni\x + 22.18.\x*.
\v 26 Ngokunjalo-ke kumaLevi; kakulamuntu ozathwala ithabhanekele laloba yiziphi izitsha zalo zenkonzo yalo\x + Nani 4.5-15. 2 Lan. 35.3.\x*.
\v 27 Ngoba ngamazwi kaDavida okucina amadodana kaLevi abhalwa kusukela kwaleminyaka engamatshumi amabili kusiya phezulu.
\v 28 Ngoba indawo yawo yayingasesandleni samadodana kaAroni enkonzweni yendlu yeN\nd kosi\nd*, phezu kwamaguma, laphezu kwamakamelo, laphezu kokuhlambulula zonke izinto ezingcwele, lomsebenzi wenkonzo yendlu kaNkulunkulu\x + 9.26. 2 Kho. 23.11.\x*,
\v 29 lowezinkwa zokubukiswa\x + 9.32.\x*, lowempuphu ecolekileyo yomnikelo wokudla\x + 9.29. Levi 6.20,21.\x*, lowezinkwana eziyizipatalala ezingelamvubelo, low\add okubhakwe\add* ngepani\x + Levi 2.4.\x*, lowokukhanzingiweyo\x + Levi 6.21. 7.12.\x*, lowesilinganiso sonke\x + Levi 19.35.\x* lobukhulu\x + Levi 19.35.\x*;
\v 30 lokuma ukusa ngokusa ukubonga lokudumisa iN\nd kosi\nd*, kanjalo lantambama,
\v 31 lokunikela konke kweminikelo yokutshiswa eN\nd kosi\nd*ni ngamasabatha\x + Isa. 1.13.\x*, ngokuthwasa kwenyanga\x + Hlab. 81.3. Nani 28.11.\x*, langemikhosi emisiweyo\x + Nani 29.39.\x*, ngenani, ngokwesimiso kukho, njalonjalo phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 32 Njalo azagcina umlindo wethente lenhlangano, lomlindo wendlu engcwele\x + Nani 1.53.\x*, lomlindo wamadodana kaAroni, abafowabo, enkonzweni yendlu yeN\nd kosi\x + 23.28. Nani 3.6-9.\x*\nd*.
